	(text "EBUG HEADER: POWER CONFIGURATION\n\nBattery CONNECTED (Board is self-powered):\nConnect VCC to ST-Link VTref (Pin 1 or 2).\n(Why: ST-Link safely senses your 3.3V logic levels without injecting external power).\n\nBattery REMOVED (Bench testing):\nConnect VCC to ST-Link 3.3V Supply (Pin 19).\n(Why: ST-Link acts as the main power supply to run your board).\n\nWARNING: Never connect Pin 19 while the battery is installed to avoid a power collision!"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 223.52 62.484 0)
